name: One Abbi Row for CAL Crew GoBears Roy ©
description:
We're sorry to say poor Ray met his fate, due to licensing requirements and corporate red tape.

Although we looked forward to sharing this swell guy, we're happy to report he's content and quite happy in a big blue copyright sky.

His visit was brief, too short some would say, but thankfully his presence motivated us in a fantastic creative way.

So keep a lookout for something new from One Abbi Row,
We'll be back - We promise with gusto and gear in tow.

To those of you who showed interest in our dear departed friend, we thank you, we're grateful and please Bear with us as we take time to mend.
(Sorry for the rhyme, we couldn't resist and sincerely hope you won't hold it against us).  

See you sooner than later!
One Abbi Row

We wholeheartedly support small business.
West Coast Designz & BYOG (California Made)
